            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%B2%E6%95%85%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%9C%E5%BC%98%E5%A6%BB%E6%A2%81%E9%B3%B3%E5%84%80-5-600%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%E8%A5%BF%E7%87%9F%E7%9B%A4%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%97kensington-hill%E8%A4%87%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%B6-8%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D9-043359308.html",
